body.p: The following Scandinavians have bought or sold properties:
1. West Town: Erie St., west of 46th Ave., Roy Singer to Henry Christensen.
2. Wood St., north of Chicago Ave., Gusta Hansen to August Wegner.
3. Jefferson: Central Park Ave., south of Schubert Ave., O.Egeland to N.J.Schonberg. Price $4,200.
4. N. Fairfield Ave., north of Cortland St., W.M. Quinn to Michael Eriksen.
5. Henderson St. east of Forty-second Ave., A.W.Madsen to John Nelson.
6. McLean Ave., west of Ballou St., Olaf Egeland to M. Batoski. Price $3,700.
7. Sawyer Ave., north of Wrightwood Ave., John Z. Anderson to Elias Koch. Price $7,000.
8. Wrightwood Ave., north of Spaulding Ave., E.T.Thoresen to Ottelie Zichow. Price $6,600.
9. Lake: Perry Ave., north of 67th t., J.K.Hooper to Julius C.Nelson. Price $5,000.
10. Hyme Park: Erie Ave. south of 133rd St., B.A.Andersen to F.H.De La Plaine. Price $12,000.
